Test fixtures for `heictojpeg`.

Files in this folder are sourced from open-source repositories:

- `libheif-example.heic` and `libheif-example.avif`:
  `https://github.com/strukturag/libheif/tree/master/examples`
- `goheif-camel.heic`:
  `https://github.com/adrium/goheif/tree/master/testdata`
